title: News: Coughlin's Sunday Broadcast
subtitle: The NUSJ turns resentment into a weekly ritual.
new-page: true
is-card: true
tags: event
view-if: ((year = 1933 and month >= 3) or year > 1933) and news_cooldown_timer = 0 and (dnvp_votes >= 6 or radio_reach >= 2 or opposition_pressure >= 3)
